# Claude Code Preferences

## Git Commit Attribution
DO NOT add attribution to git commits.
DO NOT include "Co-Authored-By: Claude" in commit messages.
DO NOT include "Generated with Claude Code" links in commit messages.

Keep commit messages clean and professional without AI attribution.

## General Preferences
- Make commits concise and follow conventional commit format
- Group related changes logically
- Avoid unnecessary self-references or branding in code/commits
